div ke andr jo bhi element bnaoge wo uske ooper dikhega(overlay)
eg:-

diva{
    divb{
        divc{

        }
    }
}
also diva ko jo bhi ht,wdth doge wo as reference with screen hogi
but divb ko jo bhi ht,wdth doge wo as reference with diva hogi na ki whole screen
and divc ko jo ht,wdth doge wo as reference with divb hogi na ki diva